void showsDiffWhenRequestHeaderIsAbsent(){
    Diff diff =
        new Diff(
            newRequestPattern(ANY, urlEqualTo("/thing"))
                .withHeader("X-My-Header", equalTo("expected"))
                .build(),
            mockRequest().url("/thing"));

    assertThat(
        diff.toString(),
        is(
            junitStyleDiffMessage(
                "ANY\n" + "/thing\n" + "\n" + "X-My-Header: expected\n",
                "ANY\n" + "/thing\n" + "\n" + "\n")));
  }

void showsHeaders(){
    Diff diff =
        new Diff(
            newRequestPattern(ANY, urlEqualTo("/thing"))
                .withHeader("X-My-Header", equalTo("expected"))
                .build(),
            mockRequest().url("/thing"));

    assertThat(
        diff.toString(),
        is(
            junitStyleDiffMessage(
                "ANY\n" + "/thing\n" + "\n" + "X-My-Header: expected\n",
                "ANY\n" + "/thing\n\n\n")));
  }
